00:01:19.610 --> 00:01:24.570
So this just makes the point
that you can put anything at

00:01:24.570 --> 00:01:25.310
the lattice point.

00:01:25.310 --> 00:01:29.260
So there it is.

00:01:29.260 --> 00:01:30.400
Oh, here's the point.

00:01:30.400 --> 00:01:33.120
This is me at a conference
in Copenhagen.

00:01:33.120 --> 00:01:35.480
This is outside the
Admiral Hotel.

00:01:35.480 --> 00:01:38.370
And just to show you I'm always
thinking about 3.091, I

00:01:38.370 --> 00:01:40.400
came outside--

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:42.500
and this is a colleague of mine
from France, Marcelle

00:01:42.500 --> 00:01:43.620
Gaune-Escard.

